<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EyeScan Pro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="./icon's/Logo.jpg" alt="logo">
        </div>

        <div class="menu-container">
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="icon-left"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-trend-up"></i></div>
                <a href="/Buy24H"><span class="menu-label">Smart Money Buy / 24H</span></a>

                <div class="icon-right question-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-circle-question-mark-icon lucide-circle-question-mark">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                        <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                        <path d="M12 17h.01" />
                    </svg></div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <button class="tooltip-close">&times;</button>
                    <div class="tooltip-content english">
                        This feature shows you the latest smart money purchases in the last 24 hours. Smart money refers
                        to purchases made by experienced investors who often have early access to valuable information.
                    </div>
                    <button class="translate-btn">Translate to Arabic</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-item active">
                <div class="icon-left"><i class="fas fa-wallet"></i></div>
                <a href="/Holder"> <span class="menu-label">Smart Money / Holder</span></a>
                <div class="icon-right question-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-circle-question-mark-icon lucide-circle-question-mark">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                        <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                        <path d="M12 17h.01" />
                    </svg></div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <button class="tooltip-close">&times;</button>
                    <div class="tooltip-content english">
                        The Smart Money Holder feature tracks long-term investments made by sophisticated investors.
                        These are typically investors who hold assets for extended periods, indicating strong conviction
                        in their investments.
                    </div>
                    <button class="translate-btn">Translate to Arabic</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-item active">
                <div class="icon-left"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i></div>
                <a href="#"><span class="menu-label">Smart Money / Degen</span></a>
                <div class="icon-right question-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-circle-question-mark-icon lucide-circle-question-mark">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                        <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                        <path d="M12 17h.01" />
                    </svg></div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <button class="tooltip-close">&times;</button>
                    <div class="tooltip-content english">
                        The Smart Money Degen feature tracks high-risk, high-reward investments made by experienced
                        traders. These are typically short-term trades with significant volatility, often in emerging or
                        speculative assets.
                    </div>
                    <button class="translate-btn">Translate to Arabic</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-item active">
                <div class="icon-left"><i class="fas fa-chart-simple"></i></div>
                <a href="#"><span class="menu-label">Momentum Shift</span></a>
                <div class="icon-right question-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-circle-question-mark-icon lucide-circle-question-mark">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                        <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                        <path d="M12 17h.01" />
                    </svg></div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <button class="tooltip-close">&times;</button>
                    <div class="tooltip-content english">
                        Momentum Shift identifies when an asset's price movement is changing direction or accelerating.
                        This can help you spot potential trend reversals or continuation patterns before they become
                        obvious to the broader market.
                    </div>
                    <button class="translate-btn">Translate to Arabic</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-item free">
                <div class="icon-left">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-fish"></i>
                </div>
                <a href="/Whale"> <span class="menu-label">Whale & VCs Tracker</span></a>
                <div class="icon-right question-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-circle-question-mark-icon lucide-circle-question-mark">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                        <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                        <path d="M12 17h.01" />
                    </svg></div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <button class="tooltip-close">&times;</button>
                    <div class="tooltip-content english">
                        The Whale & VCs Tracker monitors large transactions made by significant holders (whales) and
                        venture capital firms. These entities often have substantial influence on market prices due to
                        the size of their transactions.
                    </div>
                    <button class="translate-btn">Translate to Arabic</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-item free">
                <div class="icon-left"><i class="fas fa-unlock"></i></div>
                <a href="#"> <span class="menu-label">Basic Features</span></a>
                <div class="icon-right question-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="lucide lucide-circle-question-mark-icon lucide-circle-question-mark">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                        <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                        <path d="M12 17h.01" />
                    </svg></div>
                <div class="tooltip">
                    <button class="tooltip-close">&times;</button>
                    <div class="tooltip-content english">
                        Basic Features include essential tools for market analysis, including price charts, volume
                        indicators, and basic screening capabilities. These features are available to all users at no
                        cost.
                    </div>
                    <button class="translate-btn">Translate to Arabic</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Add click functionality to menu items
        document.querySelectorAll('.menu-item').forEach(item => {
            item.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                // Don't toggle if clicking on question mark or tooltip
                if (!this.classList.contains('free') && !e.target.closest('.question-icon') && !e.target.closest('.tooltip')) {
                    this.classList.toggle('active');
                }
            });
        });

        // Show/hide tooltip when question mark is clicked
        document.querySelectorAll('.question-icon').forEach(icon => {
            icon.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.stopPropagation();
                e.preventDefault();

                // Hide all other tooltips first
                document.querySelectorAll('.tooltip').forEach(tooltip => {
                    tooltip.style.display = 'none';
                });

                // Show the tooltip for this item
                const tooltip = this.closest('.menu-item').querySelector('.tooltip');
                tooltip.style.display = 'block';
            });
        });

        // Close tooltip when X is clicked
        document.querySelectorAll('.tooltip-close').forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.stopPropagation();
                e.preventDefault();
                this.closest('.tooltip').style.display = 'none';
            });
        });

        // Translate to Arabic when button is clicked
        document.querySelectorAll('.translate-btn').forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.stopPropagation();
                e.preventDefault();
                const content = this.closest('.tooltip').querySelector('.tooltip-content');

                if (this.textContent === 'Translate to Arabic') {
                    // English to Arabic translations
                    const translations = {
                        "This feature shows you the latest smart money purchases in the last 24 hours. Smart money refers to purchases made by experienced investors who often have early access to valuable information.": "تعرض هذه الميزة أحدث مشتريات الأموال الذكية خلال 24 ساعة، وهي صفقات يقوم بها مستثمرون ذوو خبرة لديهم معلومات مبكرة.",

                        "The Smart Money Holder feature tracks long-term investments made by sophisticated investors. These are typically investors who hold assets for extended periods, indicating strong conviction in their investments.": "تتعقب ميزة حامل الأموال الذكية الاستثمارات طويلة الأجل من مستثمرين يملكون قناعة قوية بأصولهم.",

                        "The Smart Money Degen feature tracks high-risk, high-reward investments made by experienced traders. These are typically short-term trades with significant volatility, often in emerging or speculative assets.": "تراقب ميزة ديجن صفقات قصيرة الأجل وعالية المخاطر ينفذها متداولون متمرسون في أصول ناشئة أو مضاربة.",

                        "Momentum Shift identifies when an asset's price movement is changing direction or accelerating. This can help you spot potential trend reversals or continuation patterns before they become obvious to the broader market.": "يرصد تحول الزخم تغير أو تسارع اتجاه السعر، مما يساعدك في اكتشاف تغيرات السوق مبكرًا.",

                        "The Whale & VCs Tracker monitors large transactions made by significant holders (whales) and venture capital firms. These entities often have substantial influence on market prices due to the size of their transactions.": "يراقب متتبع الحيتان وVCs المعاملات الكبيرة التي تؤثر على السوق بسبب حجمها.",

                        "Basic Features include essential tools for market analysis, including price charts, volume indicators, and basic screening capabilities. These features are available to all users at no cost.": "تتضمن الميزات الأساسية أدوات مجانية مثل مخططات الأسعار ومؤشرات الحجم والفحص البسيط."
                    };


                    content.innerHTML = `<div class="english" style="display:none">${content.innerHTML}</div>
                                       <div class="arabic">${translations[content.textContent.trim()]}</div>`;
                    this.textContent = 'Translate to English';
                } else {
                    // Switch back to English
                    const englishContent = content.querySelector('.english').innerHTML;
                    content.innerHTML = englishContent;
                    this.textContent = 'Translate to Arabic';
                }
            });
        });

        // Close tooltip when clicking outside
        document.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
            if (!e.target.closest('.tooltip') && !e.target.closest('.question-icon')) {
                document.querySelectorAll('.tooltip').forEach(tooltip => {
                    tooltip.style.display = 'none';
                });
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>